dq_agent/
├── main.py              entry point
├── graph.py              builds the LangGraph StateGraph
├── state.py              DQState (the shared graph state) + type defs
├── config.py              paths, model name, workflow constants
│
├── agents/                LLM-backed nodes
│   ├── orchestrator.py     the supervisor
│   ├── database_agent.py   schema / PK / metadata analysis
│   ├── rule_creator.py     plans which DQ checks to run
│   └── sql_generator.py    writes DuckDB SQL for the planned checks
│
├── nodes/                  deterministic nodes (no LLM)
│   ├── validator.py         rejects anything but read-only SELECTs
│   ├── executor.py           runs SQL against DuckDB
│   └── report_writer.py       appends issues to the report
│
├── utils/
│   ├── database.py          DuckDB helpers (shared connection)
│   └── helpers.py            misc (reads the knowledge base file)
│
├── knowledge_base/
│   └── dq_checks.md          DQ check categories used by rule_creator
│
├── data/synthea_dataset/     sample tables to run against
└── output/                    dq_report.csv lands here